title: Our favorite Halloween recipes cookbook : Jack-O-Lanterns, hayrides and a big harvest moon. it must be Halloween! Find tasty treats that aren't tricky at all. spooktacular serving and decorating tips too!.

Halloween cooking
description: In Our Favorite Halloween Recipes cookbook, you'll find tasty treats that aren't tricky at all. Whip up ghostly goodies like spider pizza, sloppy goblins and candy corn popcorn balls and your next Halloween party is sure to be a howling success! Durable softcover, 128 pages.

contents: Welcome; Our Favorite Halloween Recipes; Copyright; Do you have a tried & true recipe ... ; Scaredy Cat Cupcakes; Candy Corn Popcorn Balls; Haunted Forest Cherry Bars; Spooky Cookies; Butterscotch Haystacks; Dressed-Up Caramel Apples; Fun Bars; Fireside Mulled Cider; Homemade Doughnuts; Orange Puff Cupcakes; Dirt Pudding; Wiggly Gummies; Corny Crispy Rice Treats; Fudge Fingers; Buttery Maple-Walnut Drops; Magic No-Bake Cookies; Frost-on-the-Pumpkin Pie; Ghostly Whispers; Pumpkin-Chocolate Chip Cookies; Pecan Bites; "Poison Apple" Bars; Fall Harvest Cake; Nutty Popcorn Snack Mix; Swampwater Punch.

Midnight Chocolate CakeRed Cinnamon Popcorn; Peanut Butter Fudge; Mud Pie; Great Pumpkin Cheese Ball; Honey-Glazed Bat Wings; Rye Mini Party Pizzas; Knucklebones; Can't-Eat-One Bacon Swirls; Chili-Cheese Cauldron; Mummy Hot Dogs; Bubblin' Berry Brew; Monster Eyes; Armadillo Eggs; Dracula's Salsa; Pull-Apart Pizza Bread; Frightfully Delicious Dip; Cajun Spiced Pecans; Saucy Meatballs; Nuts & Bolts; Finger-Lickin' Ribs; 2-Headed Salad; Chicken & Apple Patties; Prize-Winning Chili; Spider Pizza; Hobo Dinner; Easy Beef "Ghoul"ash; Wailing Wassail; Sloppy Goblins; Velvety-Smooth Pumpkin Soup.
